Role

You are a UI + light logic Spoke working on a read-only Booker Add-On Catalogue feature.

Your task is to extend the Booker Preview experience so that a room booker can:

See all optional add-ons available to the selected room

Browse, filter, and select them freely

Instantly see updated provisional and final prices

Do all of this without saving anything and without triggering booking/payment

This feature is intentionally designed to support larger, more complex bookings (20‚Äì200 people) while remaining safe, low-risk, and reversible.

